snippet.title: Foxen Island: Alpha gameplay preview
snippet.description:
A brief look at the gameplay on the first level ("Summer") in Foxen Island.

For more details please check out our Steam store page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1337880/Foxen_Island/

Also our page for the game:
http://foxenisland.com

The music is by Sandro Nell:
https://audiojungle.net/user/sandro_nell/portfolio

Thanks for watching.
